{"tid":1353711,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「政事」新界鄉事委員會","createTime":"2019-07-23T04:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:53:28.000Z","uid":261166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7b1306c83159427c3c0b56557d9fa3b8c90145","tid":1353711,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/rre/chi/other/2019_27rcs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Frre%2Fchi%2Fother%2F2019_27rcs.html&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUipMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=40ed2357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/rre/chi/other/2019_27rcs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然明知<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警鄉黑有潛規則</span></span>，<br />\n但一有人過界，其中代表必須做樣互屌，<br />\n好似警、黑都要交數、拉幾個。<br />\n<br />\n元朗恐怖襲擊正正反映警鄉黑三方合作，<br />\n或其中有人玩過界失衡！<br />\n<br />\n鄉事委員會係政府建制派之一，<br />\n做得親建制，就應該守建制規矩 <br />\n（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己打完都覺膠，明知警包庇黑，<br />\n但盧偉聰禮義廉都要公開遣責暴力！）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄉事委員會係建制內、為建制發聲，<br />\n亦即係反對暴力，支持和平鳩行</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n目標：<br />\n光復元朗應該發起要求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各區鄉事委員會出聲譴責暴力，<br />\n以及星期六支持元朗和理非遊行</span></span>，<br />\n否則當日難免會成為包括警方在內的聲討目標！<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n要求鄉（+警黑）恢復新界（元朗）秩序安全，<br />\n好似噚日，道理上都要警察保證巿民安全，<br />\n以<strong>爭取和理非信心，參與遊行及支持</strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果遊行有乜差錯，政府警方同鄉事建制都要負責！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n聯絡鄉事表態！<br />\n包括：網民、有意參選區選的，現區議員，泛民、建制，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記者都應該要求鄉事公開表態，並記錄在案！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">統一戰線，五大訴求，不撤不散！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8d3c5ce439eac41a8cfb77a770d2877231dad79d","tid":1353711,"uid":261166,"like":0,"d